name: AUTOGEDDON
description: @garethwild | Photograph of a busy roundabout in London - AUTOGEDDON is spray painted on a wall in the foreground. This image was included in a group show "YR.1: A Snapshot of Britain in the 21st Century" at The Photographer's Gallery London in 2001. High resolution digital scan from 35mm film transparency. Size: 3724 x 2449 px
